title: CLASSY LOW THIA KHIANG CELEBRATES PM LEE'S BIRTHDAY DESPITE POLITICAL DIFFERENCES
text:
CLASSY LOW THIA KHIANG CELEBRATES PM LEE'S BIRTHDAY DESPITE POLITICAL DIFFERENCES Submitted by farhan on 
Dear All Singapore Stuff, Advertisement 
Minister Tan Chuan Jin shared a Live video of MPs in Parliament celebrating PM Lee's birthday. If you look closely, not only PAP MPs are clapping but WP Opposition MPs too! 
If you watch the video, some PAP MPs are clapping but their faces are like stoned and so forced. Compare it with Mr Low Thia Khiang and his very genuine clapping and smile when PM Lee blows out his cake. 
Even though both men crossed swords on many issues in Parliament, Mr Low remains classy and celebrates the Prime Minister's birthday in earnest. Such behaviour is rare and worthy to highlight. 
Respect you Mr Low Thia Khiang and bless you with good health and happiness. 
Mdm Chow A.S.S. Contributor
